  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0dd1\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db6\u0dd9\u0daf\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dda \u0d9a\u0da7\u0dba\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Expanding gas distribution activities",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The company says that the distribution of Litro gas throughout the island will continue. The company also mentions that the gas distribution will be further expanded from yesterday (14th)."
      ],
